It also fails with non-self-closing tags (which <em>is</em> valid in HTML5)<br />
<br />
E.g. it converts:<br />
<pre><code>&lt;audio controls=&quot;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;source src=&quot;my.mp3&quot; type=&quot;audio/mpeg&quot;&gt;
&lt;/audio&gt;</code></pre>

to:<br />
<pre><code>&lt;audio controls=&quot;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;source src=&quot;my.mp3&quot; type=&quot;audio/mpeg&quot;&gt;&lt;/source&gt;
&lt;/audio&gt;</code></pre>

which is invalid.<br />
